reviewText: I was beyond relieved when I found this copy of Saban's Adventures of Pinocchio Vol. 2.  After I accidentally broke my old copy of this VHS by rewinding and playing it too many times, I was devastated because I thought I'd never find another one.  What a miracle that I did.  I'll NEVER make the same mistake again!  It came on time, the running time was 90 min. as it said, and the picture quality was 100%.  I'm very satisfied.
